c effects of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/91671/', '', 'Vilazodone, Sertraline, Paroxetine, St. John''s Wort, Nefazodone, Oxitriptan, Mirtazapine, Viloxazine, Milnacipran, Vortioxetine, Tryptophan, More', 'Ketotifen, Fexofenadine, Loratadine, Desloratadine, Azelastine, Terfenadine, Astemizole', 1767369485);
